\c 17
\s Mika nezvifananidzo zvake
\p
\v 1 Zvino kwaiva nemurume wegomo raEfuremu\x + 17.8. Josh. 24.33.\x*, uye zita rake \add raiva\add* Mika\x + 17.4. 1 Madz. 22.8.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino wakati kuna mai vake: Masirivha mazana gumi nezana rimwe akatorwa kwamuri, amakatuka nekuda kwawo, mukataurawo munzeve dzangu, tarirai, sirivha iyoyo ineni; ini ndakaitora. Zvino mai vake vakati: Wakaropafadzwa kuna Jehovha, mwanakomana wangu\x + 1 Sam. 15.13.\x*!
\v 3 Wakati adzosa masirivha mazana gumi nezana rimwe kuna mai vake, mai vake ndokuti: Ndaeresa zvekueresa sirivha iyi kuna Jehovha kubva muruoko rwangu kuva yemwanakomana wangu, kuti ndiite chifananidzo chakavezwa\x + Eki. 20.4.\x* uye chifananidzo chakaumbwa nekunyungudusa\x + Rev. 19.4.\x*. Zvino ikozvino ndichaidzosera kwauri.
\v 4 Asi wakadzosera mari kuna mai vake. Mai vake ndokutora zvimedu zvesirivha mazana maviri, ndokuzvipa kumuumbi\x + Isa. 40.19. 46.6.\x*; iye ndokuita nazvo chifananidzo chakavezwa\x + Eki. 20.4.\x* nechifananidzo chakaumbwa nekunyungudusa\x + Rev. 19.4.\x*; zvikava mumba maMika\x + 17.4. 1 Madz. 22.8.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino murume uyu Mika waiva ane imba yevamwari; ndokuita efodhi\x + 8.27. 18.14,17.\x* neterafimi\x + Gen.. 31.19.\x*, ndokueresa umwe wevanakomana vake kuti ave mupristi wake.
\v 6 Mumazuva iwawo kwaiva kusina mambo kwaIsraeri\x + 18.1. 19.1. 21.25.\x*; munhu umwe neumwe waiita sezvakanaka pameso ake\x + 21.25. Det. 12.8.\x*.
\p
\v 7 Zvino kwaiva nejaya raibva kuBheti-Rehemu-Judha\x + 12.8,10. 19.1. Gen.. 35.19, Josh. 19.15.\x*, remhuri yaJudha; uye raiva muRevhi, uye rigerepo semutorwa.
\v 8 Zvino murume uyu wakabva kubuda muguta, kubva paBheti-Rehemu-Judha kunogara semutorwa paaiwana \add nzvimbo.\add* Zvino wakasvika panyika yegomo reEfuremu paimba yaMika\x + 17.8. Josh. 24.33.\x* pakuita nzira yake.
\v 9 Mika ndokuti kwaari: Unobvepi? Iye ndokuti kwaari: Ndiri muRevhi weBheti-Rehemu-Judha, ndinoenda kunogara semutorwa pandingawana \add nzvimbo\add*.
\v 10 Mika ndokuti kwaari: Gara neni, ugova kwandiri\x + 18.19.\x* baba uye uve mupristi\x + 18.19. Gen.. 45.8. 2 Madz. 5.13.\x*. Zvino ini ndichakupa zvimedu zvesirivha gumi pagore\x + 11.40.\x* nenguvo dzekupfeka nezvekudya zvako. MuRevhi ndokuenda \add naye\add*.
\v 11 Zvino MuRevhi wakatenda kugara nemunhu uyu; jaya ndokuva kwaari seumwe wevanakomana vake\x + Eki. 2.21.\x*.
\v 12 Mika ndokueresa muRevhi\x + 17.5.\x*, jaya ndokuva mupristi wake\x + 18.30.\x*, uye rakava mumba maMika.
\v 13 Zvino Mika wakati: Ikozvino ndinoziva kuti Jehovha achandiitira zvakanaka, zvandava nemuRevhi ari mupristi.